location.fullValue: Plan 3 - 1973 Plan, The Ridge at Valley Knolls

data.description: Well kept home in the Sunridge Springs gated golf community, backs up to hole 12. Views of golf course lakes, Carson Valley and the Sierra Mountains. Features central A/C, new carpet, plank flooring, gas fireplace, great room plus family room design, separate laundry room with sink and cabinets. Backyard features pavers, rod iron fencing and shade trees; provides a nice sitting area to take in the views.
